profile: "Spacey is a full service interior design company specializing in residential, commercial and hospitality interiors. We provide hands-on interior design services that are tailored according to customer requirements. Our design approach considers every aspect of the process so that each element of the architectural approach progresses logically. From structural space planning to furniture layouts, selection of materials, lighting design, we balance it all to create spaces that are unique to their owners.
